node.text:
“Once upon a time a dress so fine…”
16 artists from around the world, distilled into one vision for the Maison’s latest Haute Couture show. Discover the Valentino Des Ateliers Backstage Story, an exploration into the process and symbiotic relationship between painters and Valentino’s Creative Director, Pierpaolo Piccioli.

Words and concept by GLR
Filming and editing by @ginevraag 
Music: Goldfinch- Flight to the north

node.text:
Fashion is linked to the body and to movement.
Art, however, is completely free from constraint.
@pppiccioli’s latest #ValentinoHauteCouture show, #ValentinoDesAteliers, brings art into conversation with fashion, transmuting surfaces, animating works into motion.
Experience the entire collection, shown this evening in Venice’s Gaggiandre, Arsenale, and set to the sounds of @cos1ma.

27 hand-crafted roses and the meticulous attention to craft each one.

Chapter 4 of the Maison’s “Mastery Tales” reveals the process behind the Valentino Rose Blossom Caban, rendered in the classic Valentino Rosso color.

Shop the Caban now among other floral-embellished looks via the link in bio.

Shop the bag in a special blue color along with red, white, black and pink on Valentino.cn, or by visiting Valentino Tmall Luxury Pavillion, WeChat or Valentino China boutiques.

Haven’t had enough? 

#ElsaxValentino

​
Brand Ambassador @layzhang celebrates the Maison’s latest capsule collection, made especially for Chinese Valentine’s Day.​
​
Inside a color-drenched Karaoke, Lay presents the new collection, offered in a palette of red and white and featuring heart-shaped designs on some of the Maison’s most iconic pieces.​​
​
